275
00:29:17,060 --> 00:29:19,290
Do what your heart tells you. Whatever that is.

276
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:24,460
Get in.

277
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:35,810
You said you'd do anything for him. Is this what's best for him?

278
00:29:36,810 --> 00:29:39,010
I don't think that's any of your business.

279
00:29:55,660 --> 00:29:57,260
Oh, her?

280
00:29:58,030 --> 00:30:00,130
She had a consultation and left a little while ago.

281
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:29,530
There's something magical about sunset.

282
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:31,000
(For rent)

283
00:30:32,830 --> 00:30:35,470
New buildings and old ones,

284
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:41,380
