295
00:31:53,250 --> 00:31:54,410
Because you think without him,

296
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:57,320
I won't be okay?

297
00:31:58,290 --> 00:31:59,290
No.

298
00:32:00,550 --> 00:32:01,920
Without you,

299
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:04,060
I don't think he'll be okay.

300
00:32:08,660 --> 00:32:11,800
You know what a mess he is.

301
00:32:14,170 --> 00:32:15,270
Sometimes...

302
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:19,010
I even miss his awful jokes.

303
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:22,280
You're right.

304
00:32:23,410 --> 00:32:24,880
They're really not funny.

305
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:34,020
He...

306
00:32:35,090 --> 00:32:38,130
