307
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:30,280
Look at the state of you.

308
00:33:33,710 --> 00:33:34,750
I thought you said I looked fine.

309
00:33:37,250 --> 00:33:39,050
You really are a mess without me.

310
00:33:41,690 --> 00:33:42,820
I know.

311
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:46,760
Without you,

312
00:33:48,330 --> 00:33:49,330
I'm a mess.

313
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:53,300
So...

314
00:34:01,510 --> 00:34:02,510
So, please...

315
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:05,410
don't leave me.

316
00:34:24,530 --> 00:34:27,470
You win everything you touch. Good heavens.

317
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:34,470
What's with the surprise visit? You didn't even call.

318
00:34:35,680 --> 00:34:36,740
