410
00:42:44,160 --> 00:42:45,670
A one-night mistake.

411
00:42:48,770 --> 00:42:51,770
After Do Hyun and I broke up, I was struggling and so lonely.

412
00:42:54,270 --> 00:42:56,040
And I was only 20 back then.

413
00:42:57,510 --> 00:43:00,880
