415
00:43:08,860 --> 00:43:11,220
That's why I decided to have Daniel.

416
00:43:14,090 --> 00:43:15,630
I guess that must be why...

417
00:43:16,530 --> 00:43:20,230
I tricked myself into thinking Do Hyun could fill this emptiness.

418
00:43:22,240 --> 00:43:23,370
But you know, Yoon Ju...

419
00:43:26,110 --> 00:43:29,740
loneliness doesn't give you a free pass.

420
00:44:04,580 --> 00:44:05,580
All this time,

421
00:44:11,520 --> 00:44:12,590
it's been great.

422
00:44:16,390 --> 00:44:17,390
Thanks to you.

423
00:44:24,330 --> 00:44:25,570
I didn't know you could talk like that.

424
00:44:34,340 --> 00:44:35,340
So now,

425
00:44:38,110 --> 00:44:39,680
are you not going to call me Dad anymore?

426
00:44:58,970 --> 00:45:00,200
I should get going now.

427
00:45:12,110 --> 00:45:13,810
Be happy with Jun Kyung.

428
00:45:18,780 --> 00:45:19,790
Okay.

429
00:45:26,390 --> 00:45:28,190
I think I'm going to miss you a lot.

430
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:34,500
Dad.

431
00:46:19,610 --> 00:46:21,510
I wish I could've treated you to somewhere nicer.

432
00:46:22,320 --> 00:46:24,020
What could possibly be better than this?

433
00:46:26,820 --> 00:46:28,920
I'm so glad you seem to be okay.

434
00:46:30,520 --> 00:46:31,820
I was really worried about you.

435
00:46:36,600 --> 00:46:38,230
